name: Get Out of My Orbs
description: You start off in a rooom filled with cyberdemons. You better be quick to the invulnerability orbs or they will blast you. It is inspired by "Short Death," level 2 from CrazyDoomGuy's WAD, Very Hard. Music is the same as level 11 from Dying Camel's Demons #1, "The Green Machine." Demo is available at: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZVrdrN_jirE
